  "title": "Product Development Engineer | Marine Electrical Supplies (CAD)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is an <strong>Electrical Supplies.</strong> Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Product Design Engineer to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West </strong>- easily accessible.<br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform in-depth analysis of customer expectations, industry movements, and functional specifications <strong>to guide product development</strong>.</li><li>Identify, evaluate, and develop new product concepts or external solutions to expand the organization’s product portfolio.</li><li>Create comprehensive mechanical design outputs, including technical documentation, 3D models, and engineering specifications.</li><li>Work closely with cross-functional engineering teams to align designs with performance, quality, and compliance requirements.</li><li>Determine suitable materials and production methods to optimize durability, cost, and manufacturability.</li><li>Support prototype fabrication and testing activities, using results to confirm design feasibility and performance.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Electrical Engineering, Industrial Design or a related field. </li><li>Two years in <strong>mechanical design</strong> within a product development environment.</li><li>Proficiency in CAD software (e.g., SolidWorks, AutoCAD).</li></ul><p><em>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click </em><em><strong>APPLY NOW</strong></em><em> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</em></p><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</em></p><p><em>Email Address: </em><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</em></a></p><p><em>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</em></p><p><em>EA License No: 19C9682</em></p><p><em>EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</em></p>",
